No. Oh yes, oh yes. Gutting. Gutting herring. Oh yes, she - they used to go to the east coast. Oh yes. Quite a lot of the Barra - Barra women used to go to the east coast and to the English fishing. Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid8731373 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9518286\charrsid5125818 You were born in 1888?
