No, there was what you call quack doctors, there was - three in this - in these places, up 'til lately. Yes. Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid8731373 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9518286\charrsid5125818 Would they be travelling doctors?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid8202071 DC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9518286\charrsid5125818 
No, they were getting - they were getting the job somewhere or not, I don't know. Th
ere was the one - the one that was here when I left - when I left Barra, Doctor McAuley, he was a Lewis man and knew as much about - medical as what that stool did. It did not matter and - at the time of the measles there that's what I - when I took notic
e of it, I took the measles myself.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid8731373 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9518286\charrsid5125818 So you realized he was a quack at the time of the measles?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid8202071 DC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9518286\charrsid5125818 
Yes. Yes. Because - everybody that - that he would visit - he would ask somebody in the house to go - up with him and get a bottle, and that bottle was
 - everybody that was going was getting the same thing and I heard them saying several times - although I was taking no notice of it at the time telling the honest truth - it was only treacle and water mixed.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid8731373 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9518286\charrsid5125818 People said that at the time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid8202071 DC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9518286\charrsid5125818 Yes. Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid8731373 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9518286\charrsid5125818 But they still went on using him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid8202071 DC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9518286\charrsid5125818 Well there you are. There was no other - there wasn't remedy for it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid8731373 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9518286\charrsid5125818 Did your mother not make medicines herself then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid8202071 DC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9518286\charrsid5125818 Oh no, no, no, no I never seen anything like that. I never seen any - nob
ody making any medicine. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid8731373 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9518286\charrsid5125818 So there was one sister older than you and then you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid8202071 DC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9518286\charrsid5125818 Yes. Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid8731373 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9518286\charrsid5125818 How many after that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid8202071 DC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9518286\charrsid5125818 
Well - Mary, Thompson, Neil who lives up there - by the Post Office. Yes. Neil. Rlec. Micheal. Now Michael - and Alec, t
hey were in the States, because Alec was torpedoed in the Scottish Monarch in 1915. And when he got ashore - and joined another ship and he landed in New York. And he cleared out of New York. Cleared out in New York. And he went through to Ohio. And when 
h
e - when he - the - the Yanks joined the war he joined and all. And he came to France. And he was in France for a year - eighteen months. He got leave before how would go back, and he came home here. And nobody knew him. In fact I wasn't at home at the ti
me. I was at the war the same as themselves. And nobody knew him. He was in }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid3034638\charrsid5125818 Yankee}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9518286\charrsid5125818  uniform you see. Well he went back again to the States and - he was - he never came back to - to France. And he married - in New Jersey. New Jersey - Trent - Trenton, New Jer
sey. And - his wife - he died and Michael died - Michael died in New York as well and his wife still is in - what they called Chester, Philadelphia.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid8731373 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9518286\charrsid5125818 What work did he have over there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid8202071 DC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9518286\charrsid5125818 He was in the - rubber works, I don't know what as, I don't know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid8731373 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9518286\charrsid5125818 Before that did he do fishing round here?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid8202071 DC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9518286\charrsid5125818 
That's all, that's all, before - before he - before the war started. And he never - he never - bothered no more with the - merchant ship - British - British merchant ship.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid8731373 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9518286\charrsid5125818 And there's also another one in the States you said?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid8202071 DC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9518286\charrsid5125818 Michael. Michael. Michael. Michael and Alec.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid8731373 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9518286\charrsid5125818 What did Alec do there then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid8202071 DC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9518286\charrsid5125818 
That's Alec I'm telling - Alec and - Michael, he was in the - he was in some hotel, I don't know. The later end - the last - last time anyway, before he died he was in some hotel in New York. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid8731373 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9518286\charrsid5125818 What was his job in the hotel, do you know?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid8202071 DC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9518286\charrsid5125818 No, I don't know. I don't know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid8731373 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9518286\charrsid5125818 There were no more sisters?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid8202071 DC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9518286\charrsid5125818 No. Oh yes, yes, yes, yes, yes. Oh yes, yes, I had another sister, 
