 - they had a - a big house. The grandfather. Oh yes. Oh Lord yes. He had three rooms.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid8731373 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9518286\charrsid5125818 Did they have land with it though, did they have sheep?
