Never hungry, never, never. Never hungry. Just the food that was there, it was - it was pure. It was the natural food. Compared for - to what we are getting today. You're not getting - we'r
e not getting it anyway. You agree with that? Yes. It's not now - it's not natural food at all.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid8731373 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9518286\charrsid5125818 Did you have tinned foods at that time?
