No, no, I never seen a tin in my life. No, no. No, the only tin that you'd see there was an occasional - condensed milk. Tin of condensed milk. Yes. That's the only tin. And an occasional corned - corned }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid3034638\charrsid5125818 beef}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9518286\charrsid5125818 , what was - Libbys. Yes.
