h one year that I cut peats over there, one year. Getting the - getting coal then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid8731373 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9518286\charrsid5125818 You had coal before the first world war?
