Yes. Yes. Yes. I can remember - I think when I went to school - I remember one winter being - barefooted, frost on the ground, ice. Yes, I can remember that. I don't know what age I would be. Going on to eight or ten - at the time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid8731373 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9518286\charrsid5125818 They would be mended by your father?
