ied. See? That this was going to be my - headquarters. See? Either in Barra or in Vatersay. See? But - now - since I brought up my family here - they're away. They're married now in Glasgow. Two of them. One of them in Oban. Now - today, six years ago, th
e wife and I - or seven years ago - when when I - when the - the - the youngest one got married. The first winter after she got married we got to go out.
